{"tid":1314560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞雙匪當街劫大肚婆　用布笠頭強搶現金及手機","createTime":"2019-07-14T08:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T05:32:37.000Z","uid":161728,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8028dd01a67f1c2f6b089dcab575cd6f8aa8b96c","tid":1314560,"uid":161728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"南亞幫又作奸犯科，當街搶劫大肚婆！今日(14日)凌晨零時許，一名姓葉(26歲)孕婦，途經馬頭角道與九龍城道交界一公廁對開，突有2名南亞裔男子從後撲出，用布笠頭將她推倒，她頓失平衡跌坐地上，繼而遭對方搶去手袋，內有4,000港元現金及一部約5,000港元手機。賊人得手逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警員聞訊趕至兜截，惜無發現。女事主手腳擦傷，由救護車送院治理。案件列作搶劫，交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進，涉案賊人年約25至30歲，警方設法追緝賊人歸案。"},{"pid":"ccb3328c5f629f758de02b0577a276f8f7f807fd","tid":1314560,"uid":161728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWCvmA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWCvmA4.png&h=5bc39fb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c564415ec15d99c05556e8d1067bd33b6af6ab7d","tid":1314560,"uid":61999,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>三毛出廢post，唔洗覆</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee22820637927c4e9ae95986b56ae089f015da11","tid":1314560,"uid":12265,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c564415ec15d99c05556e8d1067bd33b6af6ab7d","tid":1314560,"uid":61999,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>三毛出廢post，唔洗覆</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"一樣還一樣，如果單野係真咁好有問題喎，難道佢地種族有一部分人出過黎就代表佢地成個種族可以係香港殺人放火？"},{"pid":"3ec09a807ec97a9e92f85a424af0d63c17f293ce","tid":1314560,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c564415ec15d99c05556e8d1067bd33b6af6ab7d","tid":1314560,"uid":61999,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"<